{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "茶馆说书人",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "茶馆·说书人张叨叨"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "switch",
      "cases": [
        {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "flag": "heard_teahouse_story",
              "value": true
            }
          ],
          "next": "ret_open"
        }
      ],
      "defaultNext": "fv_1"
    },
    "fv_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "说书人张叨叨"
      },
      "text": "话说这崂山道士捡了本天书，正要上神仙顶，哪晓得半路上撞见一伙倒斗摸金的，从古墓头放出个大旱魃来。",
      "next": "fv_arc"
    },
    "fv_arc": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "addArchiveEntry",
          "params": {
            "bookType": "character",
            "entryId": "storyteller_zhang"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "fv_2"
    },
    "fv_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "说书人张叨叨"
      },
      "text": "那道士掐诀念咒，跟旱魃大战三百回合，直打得山摇地动，末了一把火把那东西烧成了黑炭。摸金的千恩万谢，非要拿重金酬他，道士却只一甩袖子，人就不见了。",
      "next": "fv_ch"
    },
    "fv_ch": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "sit",
          "text": "坐倒听他摆完",
          "next": "fv_sit_1"
        },
        {
          "id": "hot",
          "text": "听个闹热就算咯",
          "next": "fv_hot_1"
        }
      ]
    },
    "fv_sit_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "这道士挣钱倒撇脱得很。",
      "next": "fv_sit_2"
    },
    "fv_sit_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "说书人张叨叨"
      },
      "text": "那是撒？要是真有这门手艺，银钱还不自家往怀头钻。",
      "next": "fv_sit_flags"
    },
    "fv_sit_flags": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "heard_teahouse_story",
            "value": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "addArchiveEntry",
          "params": {
            "bookType": "lore",
            "entryId": "lore_li_tiangou_story"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "fv_sit_3"
    },
    "fv_sit_3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "说书人张叨叨"
      },
      "text": "你娃要是听得心头发痒，不如去问哈那边的瞎子李。那老东西满嘴神神鬼鬼，说不定真会点门道。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "fv_hot_1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "闹热是闹热，可也不能当饭吃嘛。",
      "next": "fv_hot_flags"
    },
    "fv_hot_flags": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "heard_teahouse_story",
            "value": true
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "fv_hot_2"
    },
    "fv_hot_2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "说书人张叨叨"
      },
      "text": "饭不好吃，故事总该听两耳朵。你要真想求个糊口的本事，去问哈那边刚坐倒的瞎子李。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "ret_open": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "说书人张叨叨"
      },
      "text": "今天这段先摆到这点。啷个嘛，听够了迈？还是已经看上别的门道了？",
      "next": "ret_ch"
    },
    "ret_ch": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "q1",
          "text": "瞎子李真会算命迈？",
          "next": "ret_q1"
        },
        {
          "id": "q2",
          "text": "城隍庙后山到底闹过啥子？",
          "next": "ret_q2"
        },
        {
          "id": "q3",
          "text": "阎王岭真有恁个邪？",
          "next": "ret_q3"
        },
        {
          "id": "q4",
          "text": "没得啥子，我就再听两句",
          "next": "ret_q4"
        }
      ]
    },
    "ret_q1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "说书人张叨叨"
      },
      "text": "会不会我可不敢打包票。不过那老瞎子见的人多，嘴皮子也溜得很。你要是想求个出路，跟他搭两句总不亏。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "ret_q2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "说书人张叨叨"
      },
      "text": "前阵子有个书生，三更半夜从庙背后抄近路，回来就说看见个白影子站在月地头唱曲，嘴里唱的还是《红楼》里头的词。",
      "next": "ret_q2b"
    },
    "ret_q2b": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "说书人张叨叨"
      },
      "text": "第二天那书生就疯疯癫癫，翻来覆去就念那一句“白茫茫大地真干净”。城里人都说，庙背后那东西不是在找活人，是在等哪个。",
      "next": "ret_q2f"
    },
    "ret_q2f": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "heard_ghost_story",
            "value": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "addArchiveEntry",
          "params": {
            "bookType": "lore",
            "entryId": "lore_ghost_mountain"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "ret_q3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "说书人张叨叨"
      },
      "text": "邪不邪我不敢拿命打包票，可那地方在城北头压起，老辈子都说活人进得去，魂未必回得来。",
      "next": "ret_q3b"
    },
    "ret_q3b": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "说书人张叨叨"
      },
      "text": "这些年偏还有人往那边钻，找金子的、找龙脉的、找短命财的，回来的人没得几个还像原来那样。",
      "next": "ret_q3f"
    },
    "ret_q3f": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "heard_yanwang_story",
            "value": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "addArchiveEntry",
          "params": {
            "bookType": "lore",
            "entryId": "lore_yanwang_ridge"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "ret_q4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "说书人张叨叨"
      },
      "text": "那就搬根板凳坐倒，老张这肚子头还有的是怪事。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
}
